Script,TwoNTPuppet
setDealerCode(`

# convention-card: 21GF-Puppet
# auction-filter: Note....2N-3C Puppet

### 2N w/Puppet and any response

Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Predict-Opening-1-Bid

### NORTH ###

# Define suit lengths
cN = clubs(north)
dN = diamonds(north)
hN = hearts(north)
sN = spades(north)

# Calculate strength for North -- hcp plus 1 for every card over 4 in any suit 
nlp1 = sN>4 ? sN-4 : 0
nlp2 = hN>4 ? hN-4 : 0
nlp3 = dN>4 ? dN-4 : 0
nlp4 = cN>4 ? cN-4 : 0
strength = nlp1 + nlp2 + nlp3 + nlp4 + hcp(north)

# Define objective
weak = strength<5
game = strength>4
slam = strength>10

# Define responses
puppet = shape(north,44xx+43xx+42xx+34xx+33xx+32xx+23xx -any 8xxx -any 7xxx -any 6xxx) and game

Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Leveling

##### Level the deal #####
levGame = game and keep25
levSlam = slam and keep
levelTheDeal = levGame or levSlam

### Do it ###
twoNT and puppet and game
and levelTheDeal

### Generate Statistics ###
generate 20000000
produce 1000

action
#printoneline,

average "Game         " 100 * game,
average "Slam         " 100 * slam,

`,"S",true)
Script
Button,2N - Puppet,\n\
--- 20-21 Notrump with Puppet and any continuation.\n\
The responder's strength -- game or slam -- is leveled.\n\
%TwoNTPuppet%,backgroundColor=lightpink